// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0572 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 52f78aac-0ef5-5e7d-a6c8-5f4fe9254aca

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
